<Default><b>- What would you do by knowing?</b></Default>

c0000486
00:19:24.910 --> 00:19:26.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, nothing, really.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:19:26.420 --> 00:19:27.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just curious.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:19:27.790 --> 00:19:29.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000489
00:19:31.050 --> 00:19:32.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Choco cornet.</b></Default>

c0000490
00:19:32.340 --> 00:19:33.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You asking me to get you one?</b></Default>

c0000491
00:19:34.010 --> 00:19:35.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's not it.</b></Default>

c0000492
00:19:35.880 --> 00:19:37.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kunimi gave me one one day
that I didn't bring</b></Default>

c0000493
00:19:37.800 --> 00:19:39.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a lunch to school.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:19:39.430 --> 00:19:41.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was during the first term
of our first year</b></Default>

c0000495
00:19:41.810 --> 00:19:44.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the first time I attempted
to purchase bread.</b></Default>

c0000496
00:19:44.930 --> 00:19:46.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I ended up getting
really overwhelmed</b></Default>

c0000497
00:19:46.980 --> 00:19:48.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but then he called out to me.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:19:48.100 --> 00:19:49.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000499
00:19:49.980 --> 00:19:52.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're a girl so you must like
sweet things, right, Futaba?</b></Default>

c0000500
00:19:52.940 --> 00:19:54.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- He said while eating
his battle trophy,</b></Default>

c0000501
00:19:54.990 --> 00:19:56.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the curry bread.</b></Default>

c0000502
00:19:56.400 --> 00:19:58.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The renowned prince
of curry bread, huh?</b></Default>

c0000503
00:19:58.360 --> 00:19:59.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000504
00:19:59.740 --> 00:20:00.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And then?</b></Default>

c0000505
00:20:00.950 --> 00:20:02.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nothing else.</b></Default>

c0000506
00:20:02.790 --> 00:20:04.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How much is a choco cornet?</b></Default>

c0000507
00:20:04.290 --> 00:20:05.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- 130 yen.</b></Default>

c0000508
00:20:06.040 --> 00:20:08.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Your price
is surprisingly reasonable.</b></Default>

c0000509
00:20:08.210 --> 00:20:09.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If it was you who gave
it to me,</b></Default>

c0000510
00:20:09.960 --> 00:20:11.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't have fallen in love,
though.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:20:11.460 --> 00:20:13.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It comes down to looks, then.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:20:14.170 --> 00:20:16.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In the end I think it
was all about timing.</b></Default>

c0000513
00:20:16.800 --> 00:20:19.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because I was kind of depressed
at the time.</b></Default>

c0000514
00:20:19.220 --> 00:20:21.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you want to watch
you should go and watch.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:20:21.220 --> 00:20:22.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
So anyway,</b></Default>

c0000516
00:20:22.890 --> 00:20:24.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what is it you want from me?</b></Default>

c0000517
00:20:25.140 --> 00:20:27.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Right now Futaba's staying
at my place.</b></Default>

c0000518
00:20:27.440 --> 00:20:30.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
That makes sense.</b></Default>

c0000519
00:20:30.230 --> 00:20:32.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that's why you were acting
so strange when we were on</b></Default>

c0000520
00:20:32.570 --> 00:20:33.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the phone last night.</b></Default>

c0000521
00:20:33.940 --> 00:20:36.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So what do you make
of the current situation?</b></Default>

c0000522
00:20:36.780 --> 00:20:39.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Let me ask this.
Do you think I'm a fake?</b></Default>

c0000523
00:20:39.950 --> 00:20:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That is what I thought
at first, honestly.</b></Default>

c0000524
00:20:42.370 --> 00:20:43.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But talking like this,</b></Default>

c0000525
00:20:43.530 --> 00:20:45.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know you're both
the real Futaba.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:20:45.330 --> 00:20:47.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Does the other me have
a hypothesis?</b></Default>

c0000527
00:20:47.750 --> 00:20:49.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Something about
quantum teleportation,</b></Default>

c0000528
00:20:49.870 --> 00:20:51.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if that's an actual possibility.</b></Default>

c0000529
00:20:51.710 --> 00:20:54.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then it looks like we've come
to the same conclusion.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:20:54.670 --> 00:20:56.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Based on what she shared
from our observations,</b></Default>

c0000531
00:20:56.880 --> 00:20:59.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what she thought was most likely
is that your own consciousness</b></Default>

c0000532
00:20:59.970 --> 00:21:02.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is what's observing you and that
there are two copies of it</b></Default>

c0000533
00:21:02.220 --> 00:21:03.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for one reason or another.</b></Default>

c0000534
00:21:03.470 --> 00:21:04.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What kind of reason?</b></Default>

c0000535
00:21:05.060 --> 00:21:06.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She says she didn't have
any clue.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:21:06.930 --> 00:21:09.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She flat out lied and you
just blindly believed her?</b></Default>

c0000537
00:21:09.770 --> 00:21:11.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why do you think she's lying?</b></Default>

c0000538
00:21:11.600 --> 00:21:13.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Because I do have a clue
as to why.</b></Default>

c0000539
00:21:14.020 --> 00:21:15.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If it doesn't make
a difference who I ask,</b></Default>

c0000540
00:21:15.650 --> 00:21:16.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then tell me.</b></Default>

c0000541
00:21:17.030 --> 00:21:19.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I have to get back
to my club stuff now.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:21:19.950 --> 00:21:22.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, X and Y here are inside
the parenthesis.</b></Default>

c0000543
00:21:22.360 --> 00:21:23.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Right.</b></Default>

c0000544
00:21:23.660 --> 00:21:25.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm making coffee.
You want some?</b></Default>

c0000545
00:21:25.330 --> 00:21:27.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Y--Yes, thank you.</b></Default>

c0000546
00:21:27.370 --> 00:21:30.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede's the little sister
so honey cafe ole with lots</b></Default>

c0000547
00:21:30.250 --> 00:21:31.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of milk and honey
is her favorite.</b></Default>

c0000548
00:21:31.960 --> 00:21:33.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That sounds delicious.</b></Default>

c0000549
00:21:33.420 --> 00:21:35.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd love to have the same thing
if that's okay.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:21:35.590 --> 00:21:38.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh. Then maybe
I'll have that, too.</b></Default>

c0000551
00:21:38.260 --> 00:21:39.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cell phone ringing]
- [whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000552
00:21:39.220 --> 00:21:41.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
Sorry, Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000553
00:21:41.090 --> 00:21:42.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like it's from my manager.</b></Default>

c0000554
00:21:43.550 --> 00:21:46.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is something the matter?
 - Do you have a second to talk?</b></Default>

c0000555
00:21:46.100 --> 00:21:47.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, it's fine.</b></Default>

c0000556
00:21:47.430 --> 00:21:48.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thank you for your hard work</b></Default>

c0000557
00:21:48.390 --> 00:21:49.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the recent film shoot.</b></Default>

c0000558
00:21:50.140 --> 00:21:51.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you out of the house,
by chance?</b></Default>

c0000559
00:21:51.690 --> 00:21:53.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I am.
I'm at my boyfriend's.</b></Default>

c0000560
00:21:53.480 --> 00:21:55.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah, boyfriend's.</b></Default>

c0000561
00:21:55.480 --> 00:21:58.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, what? Boyfriend?
Did I hear you right just now?</b></Default>

c0000562
00:22:01.150 --> 00:22:02.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Futaba was just around, right?</b></Default>

c0000563
00:22:03.030 --> 00:22:04.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So you noticed her.</b></Default>

c0000564
00:22:04.490 --> 00:22:06.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, right after
the game started.</b></Default>

c0000565
00:22:06.240 --> 00:22:08.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Does she come by
to watch often, then?</b></Default>

c0000566
00:22:08.290 --> 00:22:09.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm, once in a while.</b></Default>

c0000567
00:22:09.870 --> 00:22:12.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>On her way too
and from club activities.</b></Default>

c0000568
00:22:12.120 --> 00:22:14.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Who knows what's actually on
the way?</b></Default>

c0000569
00:22:14.210 --> 00:22:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So is something going on
with Futaba?</b></Default>

c0000570
00:22:16.340 --> 00:22:17.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What makes you ask that?</b></Default>

c0000571
00:22:17.960 --> 00:22:19.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You don't like school
near enough to come here</b></Default>

c0000572
00:22:19.960 --> 00:22:21.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>over summer break without
a reason.</b></Default>

c0000573
00:22:22.510 --> 00:22:24.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which makes me thinks
something's going on with her.</b></Default>

c0000574
00:22:24.640 --> 00:22:25.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000575
00:22:27.760 --> 00:22:30.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- 'Kay, got it!
I'll be right there!</b></Default>

c0000576
00:22:30.930 --> 00:22:32.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If something happens,
reach out, all right?</b></Default>

c0000577
00:22:32.600 --> 00:22:34.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh?
- With Futaba.</b></Default>

c0000578
00:22:35.060 --> 00:22:37.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I was planning to even
if it's midnight.</b></Default>

c0000579
00:22:37.440 --> 00:22:39.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you better be ready
to come flying over.</b></Default>

c0000580
00:22:39.570 --> 00:22:41.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm not sure about
the flying part.</b></Default>

c0000581
00:22:41.610 --> 00:22:43.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I am pretty fast on a bike!</b></Default>

c0000582
00:22:43.700 --> 00:22:44.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000583
00:22:45.450 --> 00:22:47.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cicadas chirping]</b></Default>

c0000584
00:22:47.160 --> 00:22:49.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone trilling]</b></Default>

c0000585
00:22:49.120 --> 00:22:51.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[receiver clicks]
- Hi. Azusagawa here.</b></Default>

c0000586
00:22:51.160 --> 00:22:53.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, Mai, please repeat
what you just said.</b></Default>

c0000587
00:22:53.460 --> 00:22:55.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hi, Azusagawa here.</b></Default>

c0000588
00:22:55.670 --> 00:22:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I wanna hear it more like
a newlywed wife.</b></Default>

c0000589
00:22:57.840 --> 00:23:00.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How can you get so worked up
over one little phone call?</b></Default>

c0000590
00:23:00.840 --> 00:23:02.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So how are things on your end?</b></Default>

c0000591
00:23:02.460 --> 00:23:04.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She was indeed here
at school today.</b></Default>

c0000592
00:23:04.550 --> 00:23:07.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see. She's been here
the whole time, too.</b></Default>

c0000593
00:23:07.390 --> 00:23:09.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> Anyway, can you come home soon?</b></Default>

c0000594
00:23:09.890 --> 00:23:11.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Something the matter?</b></Default>

c0000595
00:23:11.520 --> 00:23:13.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I got a call
from my manager earlier</b></Default>

c0000596
00:23:13.640 --> 00:23:14.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and there's something
I really want to talk</b></Default>

c0000597
00:23:15.020 --> 00:23:16.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to you about in person.</b></Default>

c0000598
00:23:16.350 --> 00:23:18.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- To me?
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000599
00:23:18.310 --> 00:23:20.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's wrong?
- Oh, it's nothing.</b></Default>

c0000600
00:23:20.440 --> 00:23:21.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I'll see you later.</b></Default>

c0000601
00:23:25.610 --> 00:23:27.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000602
00:23:27.110 --> 00:23:29.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're friends with that girl,
aren't you?</b></Default>

c0000603
00:23:29.160 --> 00:23:32.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't know a "that girl"
so I'm assuming you mean Futaba?</b></Default>

c0000604
00:23:32.370 --> 00:23:33.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Isn't what she's
doing dangerous?</b></Default>

c0000605
00:23:34.000 --> 00:23:35.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like, really.</b></Default>

c0000606
00:23:35.500 --> 00:23:37.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh. How so?
- Here.</b></Default>

c0000607
00:23:37.580 --> 00:23:39.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is her hidden account.</b></Default>

c0000608
00:23:43.760 --> 00:23:44.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000609
00:23:52.850 --> 00:23:54.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000610
00:23:55.680 --> 00:23:58.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000611
00:23:58.730 --> 00:24:01.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>["Fukashigi no Carte" plays]</b></Default>

c0000612
00:24:01.650 --> 00:24:08.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000613
00:24:47.360 --> 00:24:54.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000614
00:24:56.370 --> 00:25:00.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, big brother.
You're such a rascal.</b></Default>

